fficer and president of the company effective january   and chairman of the board of directors effective july   mr bush served as president and chief operating officer of the company from march  through december  as president and chief financial officer from may  through march  and as corporate vice president and chief financial officer from march  to may  following the acquisition of trw inc trw by the company he was named corporate vice president and president of the space technology sector mr bush joined trw in  and during his career with that company held various leadership positions including president and ceo of trw aeronautical systems he is a director of norfolk southern corporation he serves on the boards of several nonprofit organizations including the aerospace industries association the businesshigher education forum conservation international inova health systems the naval academy foundation and the congressional medal of honor foundation attributes skills and qualifications  significant business experience with over  years in the aerospace and defense industry  prior leadership positions within northrop grumman including as chief operating officer chief financial officer and sector president  extensive international business experience  extensive leadership roles in community service source northrop grumman corporation on    sign up for equilar atlas and view wesley g bushs full profile by accessing equilar atlas you can view bios network salary and wealth events of industryleading executives like wesley g bush more specifically youll be able to identify corporate executives in wesley g bushs network and community follow changes in wesley g bushs employment and moneyinmotion connect with wesley g bush through your network of conections view full profile   search for over  executive profiles bio example wesley g bush wesley g bushs connections  sign up now to view wesley g bushs  connections » heidi g miller board member general mills inc james f palmer